Subject: [RFC 5/9] platform/x86: huawei-wmi: Control micmute led through wmi interface
Date:   Wed, 31 Jul 2019 13:52:51 -0400
Message-Id: <20190731175255.25676-6-ayman.bagabas@gmail.com>
